    "description": "本游戏是以卡片战斗为核心的Roguelike游戏.在每次探险中,打造属于自己的套牌流派,在构筑策略,探索地牢中展现自己的智慧吧!<br><br>讨论游戏和反馈意见可以加<strong>QQ群496051447</strong> 或者发到邮件 <a href=\"mailto:fantasyheroes@163.com\">fantasyheroes@163.com</a><br><br>游戏特色<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/4d8e6d9a7e7e2ff9339efb798b7bff1d.avif?t=1563065737\" width=616 height=102 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 特色各异的角色 </h2>  我们计划推出至少3个角色.<br>每个角色都有独特的能量值与抽牌规则,体验各不相同的战斗思路与节奏!(抢先体验中暂时只有2个角色,将来会扩充)<br>每个角色还拥有不同流派的初始套牌和各具特色的初始圣物(需要困难以上难度)可以选择!玩家可以自由的搭配属于自己的流派!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/1c8f458be5ce9df058e2b8e20ed5fad8.avif?t=1563065737\" width=618 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/195eb61f87768a52e58b367daeb83c06.avif?t=1563065737\" width=618 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 独特的卡组构筑</h2>  通过战斗,商店,冒险,获取稀有度不同的卡包,打开卡包可以选择想要加入牌组的套牌,也可以花费符文石获取额外的选择机会,或者放弃这次选择,避免牌组膨胀!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/3d2940bcd4c02ea887f6d9defe60c1a1.poster.avif?t=1563065737\" width=618 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/3d2940bcd4c02ea887f6d9defe60c1a1.webm?t=1563065737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/3d2940bcd4c02ea887f6d9defe60c1a1.mp4?t=1563065737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 独特的循环式地下城</h2>  我们将地下城事件以卡片形式部署,每次可以在3张卡片中选择1张&quot;前进&quot;到该位置,合理的规划路线,补给,和疲劳度,尽可能的搜刮地下城中的战利品吧!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/d25c280c78b8d62c64a0d89d6b8547d5.poster.avif?t=1563065737\" width=618 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/d25c280c78b8d62c64a0d89d6b8547d5.webm?t=1563065737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/d25c280c78b8d62c64a0d89d6b8547d5.mp4?t=1563065737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 独特的战斗系统</h2>  敌人并不总是只有一个,也不会总是只站成一排!横扫还是贯通?位置关系也是战斗中需要考虑的重要因素.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/d3c975c147e24c275948ac0cf4666e64.poster.avif?t=1563065737\" width=618 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/d3c975c147e24c275948ac0cf4666e64.webm?t=1563065737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/d3c975c147e24c275948ac0cf4666e64.mp4?t=1563065737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 打造/分解卡片系统</h2>  初始的卡片太弱?没关系,通过游戏中获取的资源,可以讲初始卡片升级成稀有度更高的卡片,或者将其分解,移出套牌,来巩固套牌强度.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/464d6044a9cb0eb6d49be5a071677b16.poster.avif?t=1563065737\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/464d6044a9cb0eb6d49be5a071677b16.webm?t=1563065737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/815300/extras/464d6044a9cb0eb6d49be5a071677b16.mp4?t=1563065737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >· 挑战模式</h2>  通过冒险模式解锁卡片图鉴 ,可以在将来推出的冒险模式中使用,穷尽脑汁,搭配套牌挑战高分吧!(抢先体验中不包含此模式)<br><br><br>向我们路上的前行者(杀戮尖塔)和(炉石传说)致敬!",
